---
import Layout from "@/layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">Syllabus</h1>
  <hr class="my-4 opacity-10" />

  <span class="font-semibold text-2xl text-neutral-100 block mb-4">
    Mathematical analysis in ℝ (calculus in one variable)
  </span>
  <div class="space-y-2">
    <li>Real numbers</li>
    <li>Sequences</li>
    <li>Series of real numbers</li>
    <li>Functions: limits, continuity, differentiation</li>
    <li>Taylor series and power series</li>
    <li>Integration</li>
  </div>

  <hr class="border-white/5 border-dashed border-[1.5px] my-8" />

  <span class="font-semibold text-2xl text-neutral-100 block mb-4">
    Mathematical analysis in ℝⁿ (multivariable calculus)
  </span>
  <div class="space-y-2">
    <li>The Euclidean space ℝⁿ</li>
    <li>Functions of several variables. Limits and continuity</li>
    <li>Partial derivatives and differentiability</li>
    <li>Extremum points for functions of several variables</li>
    <li>Applications: optimization and gradient descent</li>
    <li>Multiple integrals</li>
  </div>
</Layout>
